fixing after testing, changes in introduction

wake lock moved to layout-xml-file (this way is not deprecated). Handler converted to static inner class (android checker complained if it is not static), segfalut prevented (setting filter in onResume not allowed since some array was not yet initialized)
refactored color bubble popup (moved color logic from view to color-popup)
color recognition improved, color table extended (some cleanup still necessary)
color-bubble bug on samsung phones fixed.
removed color recognition test (already tested in java port of name-taht-color)
cameraView bug fixed (now also shown after screenOf/sceenOn).

awareness added that EyeCamActivity can still be created in portrait mode (when screen is switched of and on again). Portrait activity will never be shown so initialization of camera and other stuf can safely be skipped then.
updated build-infrastructure and eyecam version. minor adaptions to colors.
